# DnD Companion — Backend Controllers

Controller yalnızca HTTP sınırıdır: route tanımı, guard metadata, DTO binding, service delegasyonu. İş mantığı, Prisma ve policy **service'de** ([AUTH-003]).

Genel pipeline → `10-backend-general.mdc`; policy detayı → `12-backend-authorization.mdc`.

## Controller Stack (Sıra)

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru — tipik protected write
@Controller('campaigns')
export class CampaignsController {
  constructor(private readonly campaignsService: CampaignsService) {}

  @Post()
  @RequireVerifiedEmail()
  @HttpCode(HttpStatus.CREATED)
  create(@CurrentUser() user: AuthUser, @Body() dto: CreateCampaignDto) {
    return this.campaignsService.create(user.id, dto);
  }

  @Get(':id')
  findOne(@CurrentUser() user: AuthUser, @Param('id', ParseUUIDPipe) id: string) {
    return this.campaignsService.findOne(id, user);
  }

  @Patch(':id')
  @RequireVerifiedEmail()
  update(
    @CurrentUser() user: AuthUser,
    @Param('id', ParseUUIDPipe) id: string,
    @Body() dto: UpdateCampaignDto,
  ) {
    return this.campaignsService.update(id, user, dto);
  }

  @Delete(':id')
  @HttpCode(HttpStatus.NO_CONTENT)
  async remove(@CurrentUser() user: AuthUser, @Param('id', ParseUUIDPipe) id: string) {
    await this.campaignsService.remove(id, user);
  }
}

// ✗ Yanlış — controller'da policy ve Prisma
@Patch(':id')
async update(@CurrentUser() user, @Param('id') id, @Body() dto) {
  const c = await this.prisma.campaign.findUnique({ where: { id } });
  if (c.ownerId !== user.id) throw new ForbiddenException();
  return this.prisma.campaign.update({ where: { id }, data: dto });
}
```

## Decorator Referansı

| Decorator | Ne zaman | Global mi |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `@Public()` | Auth gerektirmeyen read (reference, auth, published gallery) | JwtAuthGuard bypass |
| `@RequireVerifiedEmail()` | Create/write campaign, character, homebrew, collection | EmailVerifiedGuard |
| `@Roles(Role.ADMIN)` | `/admin/*` controller veya method | RolesGuard |
| `@CurrentUser()` | Auth user inject | — |

Global guard'lar `APP_GUARD` — `@UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard)` tekrarı gereksiz unless override.

## HTTP Status Konvansiyonu

| Method | Başarı | Not |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `GET` | `200` | `{ data }` |
| `POST` (create) | `201` | `@HttpCode(201)` veya default |
| `PATCH`/`PUT` | `200` | Updated entity `{ data }` |
| `DELETE` | `204` | Body yok |
| Validation fail | `400` | Global filter → `details[]` |

Business rule ihlali: `409` Conflict, `422` Unprocessable (örn. `LAST_ADMIN`).

Yetki: dışarıdan read yok → service `NotFoundException`; yazma yetkisiz → `ForbiddenException`.

## Path ve Prefix

Global prefix `api/v1` — controller path'ler prefix **içermez**:

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru
@Controller('campaigns')          // → /api/v1/campaigns
@Controller('campaigns/:id/dm-notes')

// ✗ Yanlış
@Controller('api/v1/campaigns')
```

Nested resource: `campaigns/:campaignId/dm-notes` — campaignId `ParseUUIDPipe`.

Admin: `@Controller('admin/users')` + class-level `@Roles(Role.ADMIN)`.

## Request / Response Envelope

Controller service dönüşünü doğrudan serialize eder; wrapper service veya interceptor'da:

```typescript
// Service return shape (tercih)
return { data: campaign };

// Liste
return { data: items, nextCursor, hasMore };
```

Controller'da manuel envelope unutma — service tutarlı dönsün.

Hata fırlatma service'den; controller try/catch ile sarmalama (global filter yeterli).

## DTO ve Query Binding

```typescript
// ✓ Doğru
@Get()
findAll(@CurrentUser() user: AuthUser, @Query() query: ListQueryDto) {
  return this.service.findAll(user, query);
}

// ✗ Yanlış — query validate yok
@Get()
findAll(@Query('limit') limit: string) {
  return this.service.findAll({ limit: Number(limit) });
}
```

`ValidationPipe` global — DTO class tipi şart. Raw `@Body() body: any` yasak.

## Param Pipe'ları

- UUID: `ParseUUIDPipe` veya custom `ParseUuidPipe`
- Enum query: DTO `@IsIn([...])`

## Public vs Optional Auth

Reference ve homebrew galeri: `@Public()` — `user` yok; service `AuthUser | null` alır (character public read).

```typescript
@Get('homebrew/:id')
@Public()
findOne(@Param('id', ParseUUIDPipe) id: string, @CurrentUser() user?: AuthUser) {
  return this.homebrewService.findOne(id, user ?? null);
}
```

`@CurrentUser()` optional: guard public ise `user` undefined olabilir — service policy null handle eder.

## Auth Controller İstisnaları

`auth.controller.ts`:
- Login/register: `@Public()`; cookie set `res.cookie` ( `@Res({ passthrough: true })` ).
- Refresh: `@Public()`; cookie'den refresh oku.
- Logout: auth gerekli.

Refresh endpoint Bearer değil cookie — özel handler.

