## Özel Controller Örnekleri

### Invite (public + auth mix)

```typescript
@Controller('invite')
export class InviteController {
  @Get(':token')
  @Public()
  preview(@Param('token') token: string) {
    return this.inviteService.preview(token);
  }

  @Post(':token/join')
  @RequireVerifiedEmail()
  join(@CurrentUser() user: AuthUser, @Param('token') token: string) {
    return this.inviteService.join(token, user);
  }
}
```

### Auth refresh (cookie)

```typescript
@Post('refresh')
@Public()
@HttpCode(200)
refresh(@Req() req: Request, @Res({ passthrough: true }) res: Response) {
  return this.authService.refresh(req.cookies?.refreshToken, res);
}
```

## Conflict ve Business Error Response

```typescript
throw new ConflictException({
  error: 'ALREADY_MEMBER',
  message: 'User is already a member of this campaign',
});

throw new UnprocessableEntityException({
  error: 'LAST_ADMIN',
  message: 'Cannot remove the last admin from the system',
});
```

## Query DTO — Liste Endpoint'leri

Tüm `GET` listelerde `ListQueryDto` veya extend:

```typescript
export class CampaignListQueryDto extends ListQueryDto {
  @IsOptional()
  @IsIn(['name', 'createdAt'])
  sort?: string;
}
```

`limit` service'de `Math.min(query.limit ?? 20, 50)` — DTO max validator ile çift koruma.

